            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "When the medic uses Medicine to provide first aid, treat deadly wounds, treat disease, or treat drugs or poison, they gain Bodyguard and In Harm\u2019s Way as bonus feats for 1 minute, but they can only use these feats to protect the target of their Medicine check.",
